    "title": "Deprecate custom task runners",
    "description": "Deprecate the custom task runners in Nx 20 so that we can remove support for it in Nx 21.\n\nThis is too much power as plugin, we saw most people use this to provide an alternative cache.\n\nWe now provide alternative caches (s3). This is an alternative. GCP and Azure to follow.",
