    "description": "Loom: \\[Please record a Loom to introduce our proposal\\]\n\n## Problem\n\nExisting workspaces have not moved onto Crystal yet. To do so, we would want to get rid of most of the target configuration they have in their `project.json` files.\n\n## Solution\n\nTo migrate existing projects to Crystal, we should be able to take the executor options they currently have and translate them into CLI arguments\n\n### Example\n\nJest Before:\n\n```\n{\n test: {\n    executor: '@nx/jest:jest',\n    options: {\n      runInBand: true,\n      passWithNoTests: true\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nJest After:\n\n```\n{\n  test: {\n    args: [\n      '--runInBand=true',\n      '--passwithNoTests=true'\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Webpack, Cypress, Next.js\n\nPlugins like Webpack, Cypress and Next.js need more work because those require some executor options to be moved into plugins in the AST.\n\n## ",
